## `node_modules/@shared/config/grit/no-object-assign.grit`

```grit
`$fn($args)` where {
    $fn <: `Object.assign`,
    register_diagnostic(
        span = $fn,
        message = "Prefer object spread instead of Object.assign()",
        severity = "warn"
    )
}
```

## `node_modules/@shared/config/package.json`

```json
{
    "name": "@shared/config",
    "exports": {
        "./biome": "./biome.jsonc"
    }
}
```

